subtitle: Information-Based Network
description: The Information-Based Network Laboratory is one of the computer laboratories that focuses on the field of information-based network development at the Faculty of Computer Science, Universitas Brawijaya (FILKOM UB).
profiledesc: The Information-Based Network Laboratory currently focuses on four research topics, namely Wireless Sensor Networks, Distributed Systems and Cloud Computing, Cryptography and Information Security, and Infrastructure Technology.
